speaker: Messenger
text: The King comes here tonight.

speaker: Messenger
text: So please you, it is true. Our thane is coming.

speaker: Messenger
text: One of my fellows had the speed of him,

speaker: Messenger
text: Who, almost dead for breath, had scarcely more

speaker: Messenger
text: Than would make up his message.

speaker: Messenger
text: Bless you, fair dame. I am not to you known,

speaker: Messenger
text: Though in your state of honor I am perfect.

speaker: Messenger
text: I doubt some danger does approach you nearly.

speaker: Messenger
text: If you will take a homely man’s advice,

speaker: Messenger
text: Be not found here. Hence with your little ones!

speaker: Messenger
text: To fright you thus methinks I am too savage;

speaker: Messenger
text: To do worse to you were fell cruelty,

speaker: Messenger
text: Which is too nigh your person. Heaven preserve

speaker: Messenger
text: you!

speaker: Messenger
text: I dare abide no longer.

speaker: Messenger
text: Gracious my lord,

speaker: Messenger
text: I should report that which I say I saw,

speaker: Messenger
text: But know not how to do ’t.

speaker: Messenger
text: As I did stand my watch upon the hill,

speaker: Messenger
text: I looked toward Birnam, and anon methought

speaker: Messenger
text: The Wood began to move.

speaker: Messenger
text: Let me endure your wrath if ’t be not so.

speaker: Messenger
text: Within this three mile may you see it coming.

speaker: Messenger
text: I say, a moving grove.
